Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.68,0:00:03.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.18,0:00:05.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I count on you to watch the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.60,0:00:07.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.93,0:00:09.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.14,0:00:12.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran's heading for her club...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.69,0:00:14.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle's investigating an infidelity case...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.52,0:00:16.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Genta and the others haven't called me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:19.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like I can finally have some time to myself today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:23.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love is magic, attack the mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.09,0:00:26.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On Saturday nights, be sure to click on Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.43,0:00:28.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The professor and Haibara are hitchhiking?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.25,0:00:29.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inside the car awaits a suspicious couple!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.06,0:00:31.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.71,0:00:33.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.54,0:00:35.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:25.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.61,0:02:29.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Beetle broke down again, Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.32,0:02:30.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.28,0:02:35.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a presentation for new inventions in Yamanashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.16,0:02:38.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that one you attend every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.25,0:02:41.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was on my way back after the presentation...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.88,0:02:44.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it suddenly stopped running.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:48.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I called the towing company to tow away my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:52.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And they gave us a ride to the nearest bus stop, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.43,0:02:53.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hasn't the bus come yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:02:54.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:06.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I'm not getting on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:08.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you lose your wallet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.82,0:03:09.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:13.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems like I dropped it somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.16,0:03:16.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There wasn't a lot of money in it anyway, so it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.58,0:03:18.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.29,0:03:24.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You called me to ask Uncle Kogorou to pick you up, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:28.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle is out on an infidelity investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.59,0:03:30.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.22,0:03:31.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not a problem, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just have her come pick you up in a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:36.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:37.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's her, her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:41.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's taking care of your house, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:43.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That evil-eyed yawny girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:45.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:49.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For being an evil-eyed yawny girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:51.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why the hell're you there!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.82,0:03:56.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you always calling the Professor's inventions stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:57.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.62,0:03:59.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to come, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:02.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,l also had no desire to stay alone in that house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:06.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With that eerie, unknown person living next door...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.71,0:04:07.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I prefer not to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:10.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean Okiya Subaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:12.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.59,0:04:13.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He seems to be a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.26,0:04:15.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.39,0:04:18.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you ask Subaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to pick you up in his car?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:20.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:22.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know how you feel about him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:28.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suspect he's a member of what you refer to as the Black Organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.99,0:04:32.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Subaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.53,0:04:33.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:34.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I felt it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.99,0:04:38.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During that Ikkaku Rock case...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:41.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I felt that pressure coming from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:45.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:48.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Undoubtedly like the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:51.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:54.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that were true, you and I would already be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.68,0:04:55.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:05:00.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keeping him in your house so you can monitor him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:04.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using me as bait, you want to see whether he makes a move or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.27,0:05:07.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.23,0:05:08.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think I would do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:09.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:14.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't you think of an excuse and get him out of your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.36,0:05:16.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They probably used information they obtained from him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:20.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe the fact that I'm the Sherry who betrayed the organization...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:24.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the fact that you're alive when you're thought to be dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:26.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have both been exposed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:31.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, to ensure we're killed discreetly,\Nthey may already be on the move...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.42,0:05:36.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And their assassins could already be closing in on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:44.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you guys are in trouble, I could give you a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:45.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have any money, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.19,0:05:49.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:50.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're headed to Tokyo, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:51.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.44,0:05:54.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we only need to get back to Tokyo as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.03,0:05:56.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have a seat in the back, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:05:57.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:05:59.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like we've found a way to get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.12,0:06:04.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the time we make it back, come up\Nwith a reason to kick that person out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:06.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Haibara!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:10.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, you've sure saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:20.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This guy didn't get much sleep last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:22.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:28.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a little packed, but bare with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.69,0:06:30.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Packed"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.94,0:06:33.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean our luggage back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:34.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's made it a bit cramped, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:36.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, by the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:38.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you explain it to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:41.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How you knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:43.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That we had no money?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:47.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess she must've heard me talking on the phone a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.54,0:06:50.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said that I dropped my wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:55.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can hear exactly what someone's\Nsaying on the side of the road while you're driving?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:07:00.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she had stopped the car right after passing\Nus, that would have made more sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.97,0:07:03.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But instead, you stopped before you even passed us, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.72,0:07:06.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I stopped the car because...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.85,0:07:11.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw you standing at the bus stop, but\Ndidn't get on the bus when it came.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.19,0:07:16.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to say you overheard our\Nconversation after you stopped the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.57,0:07:19.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I stopped, I saw something on the old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.99,0:07:22.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That stain on his chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:26.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I spilled some cola there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:30.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that, you spilled cola while wearing your seatbelt, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:33.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since there aren't any stains in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:35.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, it must've happened recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:39.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, you would've changed while at home, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.55,0:07:44.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, you were driving until just a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:47.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I didn't see your car at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.77,0:07:52.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, as I was buying coffee from the\Nroadside vending machine a while ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.94,0:07:56.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw a tow truck towing a car away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.07,0:08:00.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I figured you had a problem with your car,\Nand called the towing company to move it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.07,0:08:03.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you had them drop you off at the bus stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:10.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You wanted to get on the bus, but realized that\Nyou lost your wallet - that's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:13.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's exactly what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.04,0:08:14.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:17.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, what do you say we get going now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.80,0:08:18.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.13,0:08:19.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:39.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quite a bit of traffic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:42.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems like there's an accident ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:44.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can take a nap until we get there, if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:46.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.66,0:08:49.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, where in Tokyo is your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.58,0:08:51.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beika City, 2nd District.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:54.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beika City?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.46,0:08:55.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.29,0:08:56.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:08:58.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We happen to be heading there as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.38,0:09:00.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beika City, 5th District...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:02.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Mouri Detective Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:06.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, so that's how it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:08.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, we're friends of his and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:13.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suddenly feel sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:17.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandpa, won't you take a nap with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:21.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please wake us when we arrive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:21.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:24.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:26.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're very suspicious, these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:28.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You saw it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.45,0:09:30.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The face of the man sitting in the passenger's seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:36.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had a large scar and an eerie look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:38.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we can't just assume they're suspicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:39.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.38,0:09:41.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the back of the driver's seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:46.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a hole...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:49.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there are two on the left side back seat's door.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:52.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid these are bullet holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.81,0:09:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I see signs of them trying to clean this up, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:10:01.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the seam of the seat cover, there still stains from the blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:02.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:04.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.99,0:10:06.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:08.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandpa was talking in his sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:09.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.95,0:10:14.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we should pretend to be\Nasleep and gather some information.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:19.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About their identities, and the reason why...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:22.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They want to visit Mouri's Detective Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:26.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:27.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who're they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:31.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The load increased while I was asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.43,0:10:32.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I picked them up along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:36.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They seem to be friends of Detective Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.85,0:10:39.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What great news for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.94,0:10:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now we won't have to blindly search for his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.48,0:10:45.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, what do you think about that brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:47.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Brat"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:51.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's always with Mouri Kogorou; the\Nbrat that goes by Edogawa Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:58.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, while I do think he has a sharp mind for a kid, why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:11:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling he's the one who's really in control of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.63,0:11:06.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a fierce monster, that brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.84,0:11:10.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we are bringing him a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:14.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we treat him well, he may happily blurt out everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.85,0:11:17.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, do you really think that'll be enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:18.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:20.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Half-kill is enough for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:22.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Half-kill!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:25.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a bit too early, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.44,0:11:26.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They need to wait some...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:31.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For my overkill.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:36.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to meet them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.58,0:11:37.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.58,0:11:41.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'll cry for joy after I show them my half-kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:46.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mine isn't your average half-kill, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.64,0:11:55.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to meet them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.89,0:11:56.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.35,0:12:00.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'll cry for joy after I show them my half-kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:05.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mine isn't your average half-kill, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:09.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:14.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be, you overheard our conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:16.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:18.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just woke up because of grandpa's snoring.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:22.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you say something you didn't want us to hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.54,0:12:25.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, if you didn't hear anything, forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.63,0:12:27.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what a traffic jam we have here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.59,0:12:31.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though we're already in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.30,0:12:33.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shall we have some tea at a drive-in diner?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.43,0:12:36.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe after a rest, the traffic jam will have cleared up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.35,0:12:41.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'd also like to ask about your relationship to Detective Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.48,0:12:46.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, that's only if you're not in a hurry to get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.11,0:12:49.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you want to get home as quickly as possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.40,0:12:52.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get out of our car and fly back yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:54.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fly back?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:55.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could we fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.87,0:12:59.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:00.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's rest at the drive-in diner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.62,0:13:03.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, mind helping me read the map?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:05.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's in the glove compartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.13,0:13:11.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A gun!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:18.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.72,0:13:22.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You hitchhiked and got in a car with bad guys!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.39,0:13:25.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, a man and a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:29.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems like they wanted you and\NDetective Mouri to tell them something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.94,0:13:31.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are they with the Black Organization?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:32.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:34.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They didn't emit that scent like the others, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:36.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They do have a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.99,0:13:39.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you still with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.70,0:13:39.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:46.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Professor is talking with them and I pretended\Nto go to the restroom so I could give you a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.75,0:13:48.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is the Professor all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:50.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:55.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In regards to our relationship, we decided to tell\Nthem that you helped us looked for our missing cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:57.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not what I mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.47,0:13:59.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they're dangerous people, you should escape now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:00.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:03.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those people said they want to half-kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're heading to your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:07.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't just leave them like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:08.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Half-kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:10.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.44,0:14:15.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Half-kill is enough. It's still too early for overkill."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.74,0:14:17.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Overkill!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.99,0:14:22.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, they'll first keep you barely\Nalive so they can probe you for information.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:25.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, they'll proceed to slaughter you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:28.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you sure they really aren't from the Black Organization!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:32.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I can't say for sure now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:37.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If their goal was to find my whereabouts, as\Nthe one who betrayed the organization...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.05,0:14:39.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:40.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.68,0:14:43.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm rushing to that drive-in diner on my skateboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:47.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be there in 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.06,0:14:50.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until I arrive, try to stall them as long as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:51.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stall them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:52.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:55.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just say you happened to meet a friend\Nwho's going back to Tokyo from Chiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:59.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you decided to go home in their car instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:03.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiba!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:08.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're at the drive-in diner between Yamanashi and Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:10.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A lie like that would be uncovered in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:14.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After they realize it's a lie, they'll surely\Nbe on guard and try to find you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:16.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:19.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, before that, we're supposed to hide somewhere in the diner?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:22.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if they don't see through our lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:25.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they aren't that smart, then there's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:30.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll call Detective Takagi to set up an ambush at the detective agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:34.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll tell him that they're dangerous people with a gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:38.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With my tranquilizer gun and soccer ball,\NI should be able to beat those two, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:40.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:43.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they're from the Black Organization...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:44.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:51.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll ride with a friend who's going back to Tokyo from Chiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.42,0:15:53.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's nice, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:55.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.17,0:15:58.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for giving us a ride up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:15:59.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.64,0:16:06.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A friend? That's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.64,0:16:07.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:08.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.56,0:16:12.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our conversation about half-kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.02,0:16:14.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems like they overheard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:19.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As you thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.57,0:16:23.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those two realized it was a lie and started searching for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.99,0:16:24.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.99,0:16:26.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.45,0:16:29.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're hiding in the restroom for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But them finding us is just a matter of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:37.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps they have a grudge against Uncle\NKogorou because of some case he solved before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.17,0:16:39.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me what those two look like!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.51,0:16:43.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The woman is wearing a knit cap and sunglasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.55,0:16:45.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her hair is parted on both sides in the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:49.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man is dark skinned and has an unshaven face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:52.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also saw a large scar on his left eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.48,0:16:55.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A large scar on his left eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:58.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're definitely not harmless people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:01.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the glove compartment of their car...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:03.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They had a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:05.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there are three bullet holes in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:07.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I even saw where traces of blood had been wiped away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:10.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Notice anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:12.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anything else...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:13.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:16.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're saying weird things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:18.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weird things?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:21.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"It's a little packed, but bare with it."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.30,0:17:25.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"If you want to get home as quickly as possible,\Nget out of our car and fly back yourself."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:26.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Packed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.68,0:17:27.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are they talking in code?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.31,0:17:32.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'll be there in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:33.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So just hang in the-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:35.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Old man, you in there!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.23,0:17:37.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you are, answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.61,0:17:39.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's occupied...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.07,0:17:42.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems like we're out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:45.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's knocking on each of the stall doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.03,0:17:45.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be done soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:47.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:51.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, I think "packed" and "fly" are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:53.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:55.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Half-kill and overkill...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.71,0:17:56.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:58.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A large scar on his left eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:03.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:04.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:06.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Answer me, will ya!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.88,0:18:08.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:08.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:15.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just use an adult-like voice and shout that\Nyou're using the toilet. I think he'll leave soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.02,0:18:19.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that guy realizes there's a woman inside, he'll be embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:21.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:27.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like the person inside must be that old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,HOW RUDE!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.83,0:18:33.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,CAN'T YOU TELL I'M USING THIS?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:34.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,YOU FREAKING PERVERT!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:39.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:41.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:51.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, this is the men's room, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.39,0:18:52.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I figured.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.85,0:18:55.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Professor couldn't possibly go in the ladies' room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.27,0:18:56.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You figured!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:19:00.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't he realize it was us by my voice!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.52,0:19:04.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there a window you can use to get out of the restroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.20,0:19:10.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:13.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you and the Professor should get out from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:15.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.83,0:19:16.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.79,0:19:18.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.58,0:19:19.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you look around, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:23.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That lady will be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.13,0:19:23.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:31.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man should also appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.06,0:19:40.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just give up and surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.68,0:19:41.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give up!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:45.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.36,0:19:47.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These two...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.78,0:19:48.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are police officers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:52.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,P-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.45,0:19:53.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Police!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:57.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why are you wearing sunglasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.54,0:19:58.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, not that long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:03.10,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I got clocked by a suspect we arrested and ended up with a black eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:03.10,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\be5\fad(250,0)}Uehara Yui (29)\N{\fs13}Nagano Prefecture Police Detective
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.92,0:20:06.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Getting away with just a black eye isn't so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.38,0:20:08.29,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,As for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.41,0:20:11.98,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,My forehead got nicked by a bullet from him, and ended up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:11.98,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\be5\fad(210,0)}Yamato Kansuke (35)\N{\fs13}Nagano Prefecture Police Detective
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:43.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, with your scars and those sunglasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.31,0:21:45.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No wonder they thought you were bad guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:49.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not long ago, we had just chased down a guy, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.38,0:21:51.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we tried to get him in the car...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.07,0:21:53.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He pulled out a concealed gun and started firing at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.86,0:21:57.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As we tried to subdue him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.23,0:21:59.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got a black eye and Kan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} injured his forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.85,0:22:03.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the bullet holes and blood inside their car were due to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.40,0:22:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, you figured out it was us pretty quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.59,0:22:09.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Packed" means a tight fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.17,0:22:11.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Fly" means to drive in Nagano dialect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.63,0:22:15.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone from Nagano who knows so much about us...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.34,0:22:19.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And has a scar on his left eye - that has to be Inspector Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.85,0:22:22.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you shouldn't joke like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:25.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the half kill and overkill talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.48,0:22:30.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We figured you mistook us as dangerous people because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.07,0:22:34.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You tried to escape even though you\Nhad no money, so we looked for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:36.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A misunderstanding?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.45,0:22:40.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By half-kill, I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.96,0:22:47.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These botamochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.54,0:22:49.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, they look delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.59,0:22:50.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.50,0:22:54.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} learned to make his botamochi from\Nhis granny, so they're the best in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.80,0:22:56.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.72,0:22:59.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does botamochi have to do with half-kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.68,0:23:03.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Botamochi is made from half-ground sweet\Nrice, so they're nicknamed half-kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.44,0:23:07.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if we fully grind or "overkill" sweet rice, we get regular mochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.27,0:23:12.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, by saying, "It's still too early for overkill"...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.53,0:23:15.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He meant it's too early to eat regular\Nmochi, which is for New Year's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.74,0:23:16.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.24,0:23:20.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagano people use terminology like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.37,0:23:27.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, they're old-fashioned terms Kan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} heard\Nfrom his granny, so he goes ahead and uses them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.67,0:23:29.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} likes shocking words like those.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.59,0:23:31.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.55,0:23:33.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened in Nagano?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.67,0:23:36.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Surely you didn't come all this way just to give us botamochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.89,0:23:38.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.01,0:23:40.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a case we can't solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.60,0:23:43.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we came to borrow your wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.85,0:23:46.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bloody...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.77,0:23:48.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mystery of the "Red Wall."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.86,0:23:50.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.23,0:23:53.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Bloody Red Wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.19,0:23:56.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mystery?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.49,0:24:01.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Instead of "Hope"...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.24,0:24:04.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's now the "Mansion of Death."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.83,0:24:08.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} wasn't trying to get help from Detective Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.92,0:24:10.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems like it was actually from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.92,0:24:13.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the Red Wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.21,0:24:16.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.42,0:24:18.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.17,0:24:20.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Human Blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.55,0:24:21.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why the hell are you here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.47,0:24:23.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Koumei!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.34,0:24:47.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.61,0:24:49.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Red Spray
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.67,0:24:55.04,Signs,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the Next Episode
